name: Heart of the Afflicted
description: The image is a personal representation of the artist about how life works. Everything done with the heart, create roots and bear fruit, sometimes yes, sometimes not. But always with the hope that something will be born despite the flaws. In art, we see a beautiful tree, born from a heart, and others that have not developed enough and have broken, leaving a void. < By Renancio Monte, made from the heart ❤️>
